description: I love how these emojis look with their raised eyebrows as if to say, “I’m not sure what you mean but colour me intrigued…” They’re trying to think about and grasp what you’re talking about, but they are just not getting it. Oh well, at least they look into it. It must be their held gaze and those raised eyebrows.   (•᷉ुε ू•᷈,) (๑•̆૩•̆) (ԾεԾ|||) (๏็ટૄ ๏็ (๏็ટૄ◟๏็ ) ಠ , ಥ ʕ ͠° ʖ̫ °͠ ʔ ໒( ” ͠° ʖ̫ °͠ ” )७
title: Colour Me Intrigued…
